data.description: Just waiting for YOU!  Turn key condition.  Move right in!!  Amazing renovation in 2014 including roof, windows, siding,  kitchen, water treatment, plumbing & electric.  HVAC, gutters & downspouts replaced in 2015.  Sewer lines from house to street replaced in 2015 - pvc with long term warranty. New well cap & fittings in 2021.   Lovely ensuite Primary Bathroom remodeled in 2021.  The heart of this home is the gorgeous gourmet kitchen featuring modern appliances, ample storage space, a center island that serves as the perfect gathering spot!  Kitchen offers open floor plan to allow the  owner to use the adjacent space as either a formal dining room or family room!  Spacious laundry room in basement (but also there's a washer & dryer Hook-up in the housekeeping closet  on the Main Level.    Finished basement is perfect for family/tv room in the larger portion with the smaller sections just right for a home gym or kids' zone.  Oversized 2-car garage  with shelving, wall organizers & work bench & access to attic with partial flooring & tons of storage.  In addition there's a multicar driveway with motion sensor lights AND a separate graveled off-street parking for cars, boats or trailer/RV.  Large .39 Acre Corner Lot.   Absolutely stunning fenced (6' cedar installed 2015), terraced rear yard with multi level entertaining areas - lower is a large wooden deck, upper level is flagstone  & 10' x 10' shed.  Truly a gardener's paradise in the backyard with 4 season plantings including a pollinator garden and arbors.  Home is located just blocks from Quiet Waters Park.  Additional information on improvement & features will be available in the Documents Tab & a brochure in the house.  Hillsmere is a Special Tax Benefit District with the $249 assessment is built into the property taxes.  The Hillsmere Homeowners Association is voluntary.  The $25 annual fee allows homeowners to utilize the most beautiful beach, picnic area on the the South River, the Marina with dock/slips, kayak rack (for an additional fee) & the Community Pool (Bond & fees required).  Ideal location convenient to stunning Quiet Waters Park, Public Library,  shopping, restaurants, downtown Historic Annapolis, City Dock & the United States Naval Academy.  Don't miss out on this beauty!! (Some photos are virtually staged).
